lead_paragraph: McKenna Brooks is a dedicated and confident young gymnast on track to make the regional competitive gymnastics team, but off-track in school where she's suddenly struggling to keep up. After a bad fall at the gym, she's determined to get overcome her challenges with the help of her loving family and friends.
